Xin,

857
00:40:12,640 --> 00:40:14,180
don't just watch me try these on.

858
00:40:14,340 --> 00:40:15,860
We're in a bridal shop.

859
00:40:15,860 --> 00:40:17,780
Can't you feel the romance in the air?

860
00:40:19,300 --> 00:40:21,460
I'm not the one getting married.
What should I care?

861
00:40:21,660 --> 00:40:22,980
Try one for me.

862
00:40:22,980 --> 00:40:24,182
I want you to look beautiful.

863
00:40:28,340 --> 00:40:30,820
Please. Pretty please.

864
00:40:39,380 --> 00:40:40,060
Zong Qing.

865
00:40:40,860 --> 00:40:41,460
Captain Wu.

866
00:40:41,582 --> 00:40:42,550
Is everything all right?

867
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:43,740
Captain Wu.

868
00:40:43,820 --> 00:40:44,580
There.

869
00:40:44,710 --> 00:40:46,020
Are you happy now?

870
00:41:01,860 --> 00:41:02,740
What's wrong?

871
00:41:03,460 --> 00:41:04,660
Do I look weird?

872
00:41:06,860 --> 00:41:08,300
No, just...

873
00:41:08,460 --> 00:41:09,460
That's really different

874
00:41:09,460 --> 00:41:10,980
from what you usually wear.

875
00:41:13,980 --> 00:41:14,860
Do I look good?

876
00:41:14,860 --> 00:41:15,740
Of course.

877
00:41:18,180 --> 00:41:20,980
So I usually look bad?

878
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:23,020
No.

879
00:41:23,980 --> 00:41:25,300
You look good in everything.

880
00:41:29,580 --> 00:41:30,580
Why are you here?

881
00:41:31,871 --> 00:41:33,060
I came to bring Zong Qing back.

882
00:41:33,060 --> 00:41:34,340
The wedding plan is canceled.

883
00:41:34,340 --> 00:41:35,460
Canceled?

884
00:41:50,821 --> 00:41:54,301
♪The vast sky and sea,
this deep blue expanse♪

885
00:41:54,991 --> 00:41:58,261
♪So deep, so boundless♪

886
00:41:58,601 --> 00:42:01,771
♪Just like your arms♪

887
00:42:02,261 --> 00:42:05,381
♪Shielding me from the dark clouds♪

888
00:42:05,671 --> 00:42:09,311
♪Always bearing it all in silence♪

889
00:42:09,311 --> 00:42:15,731
♪Even the long, long road gives me peace
when you're there♪

890
00:42:16,231 --> 00:42:20,631
♪Not one to show romance
in front of others♪

891
00:42:21,091 --> 00:42:24,181
♪You speak of dreams
with such calm simplicity♪

892
00:42:24,971 --> 00:42:29,771
♪But I know your heart
holds much deeper hopes♪

893
00:42:32,041 --> 00:42:33,881
♪I truly understand♪

894
00:42:34,371 --> 00:42:38,561
♪You speak of love so slowly♪

895
00:42:38,811 --> 00:42:44,781
♪But your eyes have already
told me everything♪

896
00:42:45,287 --> 00:42:47,977
♪Using up all my fortune♪

897
00:42:47,981 --> 00:42:52,381
♪Just to trade a lifetime with you♪

898
00:42:52,471 --> 00:42:54,691
♪Thank you for awakening♪

899
00:42:54,701 --> 00:42:59,781
♪The courage once hidden in my fear♪

900
00:42:59,921 --> 00:43:03,111
♪Turning every chance into certainty♪

901
00:43:03,441 --> 00:43:06,971
♪Turning every tie into companionship♪

902
00:43:07,051 --> 00:43:12,021
♪Blooming into brilliance
for all the years to come♪

903
00:43:12,021 --> 00:43:16,011
♪No one can tear us apart♪

904
00:43:16,201 --> 00:43:19,551
♪Each time my palm feels warmth again♪

905
00:43:19,811 --> 00:43:25,151
♪The memories return,
and I'm no longer alone♪

906
00:43:26,041 --> 00:43:30,031
♪No matter how far
across time and space♪

907
00:43:30,281 --> 00:43:33,681
♪My longing reaches you in silence♪

908
00:43:33,801 --> 00:43:38,331
♪No need to call out loudly♪

909
00:43:38,331 --> 00:43:41,001
♪No matter how much it takes♪

910
00:43:41,021 --> 00:43:45,431
♪To bring this drifting heart to shore♪

911
00:43:45,431 --> 00:43:48,691
♪Thank you for standing behind me♪

912
00:43:48,711 --> 00:43:52,761
♪Lighting up the darkness and despair♪

913
00:43:52,761 --> 00:43:56,231
♪The bigger the world,
the lonelier it feels♪

914
00:43:56,231 --> 00:44:00,001
♪Only by your side♪

915
00:44:00,011 --> 00:44:07,091
♪Can I truly feel this warmth inside♪
